    { num: 5, title: 'Water Bed or Themed Room', description: 'The Excellent offers both water bed service and scenario-based themed rooms — choose a traditional water bed experience, or pick a themed room (office, classroom, hospital, cinema, etc.). Themed rooms cost an extra MOP 440, and you can fully customize costumes and interaction style.' },
