    { num: 4, title: 'Relaxed Matching', description: "Victoria has no fixed selection shows or runway events — simply tell the manager your preferences and they'll arrange suitable therapists to meet you. The entire process moves at your own pace with zero pressure or rushing, making it the most relaxed selection experience in Macau." },
    { num: 5, title: 'Choose Your Therapist', description: 'Around 70 therapists on-site, including Chinese, Vietnamese, Japanese, and Korean nationalities. Victoria is known for meticulous, attentive service with consistently high standards. Prices range from MOP 2,298 to MOP 6,998, plus a 10% service fee.' },
